node.text: SO excited, I can't even put it in words 🙊 thanks everyone for tuning in this surprise live. The candle is now available on cocorrina.com so I wanted to share a full view and backstory of how we made it 🥰

node.text:
Our moon baby with @annarosamoschouti is now live and available for pre-order!

Anna and I did a live together to talk about this magical collaboration but also our personal stories, journey and the advice that have shaped our paths.

node.text:
Thank you to everyone who joined in today on my very first Divine Feminine Tarot live. I can't believe we are actually here and I'm finally sharing our deck with you, after a year and a half in the making! 

Theo and I are forever grateful that we are able to do this together. I hope you enjoy this deck when it reaches your hands. I poured all the magic I had and so many people worked hard to bring it to life!

node.text:
Our little Dream Journal is already 1 year old. Can you believe it? Inspired by my wildest, weirdest and craziest dreams, this will forever be the first product I ever created (yes, even before prints came into the picture!) We’re on the 3rd edition today, and my most talented friend @nibinquiel directed and shot this dreamy movie for our journal, starring @aminahibrahim

Thank you ladies for bringing the dream journal world into reality ♥️ I hope you all have only the sweetest dreams. 🎵 Catching Flies

node.text:
It has been almost a month since I held my very first deck for the first time. It took a long long journey to shed my skin and old habits in order to discover who I really am, who I’m meant to be in this life and what I’m meant to do 
And this is it. My dream has always been creating magic. It’s has always been my safe place, the spark that lives in my chest and fills me in with breath and passion

It never gets old feeling the excitement of having their magic in my hands and even more seeing how much you have been loving them. In the video, appear both the gold and holographic gold foil silk cloths 🎵 Diomede by Undroid

node.text:
Grimoire Noble Edition [Pre-order] The Grimoire, Noble Edition ✨ Giveaway 🥰

It was made for the deepest magic, the greatest witch, to last forever.

I've been dreaming for SO long to make Grimoire journals, and I'm in deep gratitude that they are finally here! The Noble edition has gilded edges and a synthetic leather hardcover with gold foil 🥲 made of dreams to hold your magic for years to come.

And of course, to celebrate, we are giving away 2 of these Grimoires! 

To enter the giveaway, tag your soulmate in the comments 🖤 each comment counts as one entry 🖤 the winners will be announced on the 4th of September at 10pm EST. Good luck to everyone!

ps. The Grimoires are currently on pre-order and will be shipped within November.

node.text:
The Cosmic Wild Oracle screenshot game + a giveaway!! Close your eyes, relax, and take a screenshot when you’re ready. See your fortune unveil in front of your eyes. 

Our very first oracle deck is now officially available for pre-order 🦌 Cosmic Wild Oracle Deck [Pre-order] ✨ I have so much love for this one; working with these animals for this deck has fought me so much the past months. It’s been a true blessing!

So many of our things went out for pre-order today; this deck, the new 2022 Aurele planner, and our collection of Grimoires 🥰 Which is why, for about 4 days, we’ll have a giveaway of each here!

THE GIVEAWAY: 

On the 3rd of September at 1 pm EST, I'll randomly pick 3 winners. You will be able to choose your animal, and we’ll send it to you as a gold foil print (all of the cards from the deck are available as prints too, just like in this video) + you win an oracle deck as well, which will be shipped in March!

TO ENTER:  tag your soulmate in the comments with an emoji of your favorite animal. 

1 tag = 1 entry. You can enter as many times you want until the 3rd; the more, the better!!!! 

Good luck, Star-shines!!!

node.text:
The Aurele 2022 planner 😭🙈 literally - my masterpiece until this day. I cannot describe the amount of work I’ve put this year, but I couldn’t be more proud of what I’ve created!

You know my planners are themed every year, and 2022 is dedicated... to magic, witches and it will bewitch you! The general layout is Grimoire-themed. It’s a book of shadows planner, with topics divided into each month. There are prompts and SO much information to learn and write your own Grimoire, but also, make your year magical every single day. I have a feeling we’re going to need it in 2022 🖤

Pre-orders open on the 31st of August and that wraps up ALL the things that are going on pre-order that day 😅 I will be sharing more of the inside, content, and sneak peeks in the following days. 

Oh and ps. This year’s planner will also have a synthetic leather hard cover woohooooo!!

The Grimoires collection 🧹🪄

I've been dreaming of making grimoires, real, magical grimoires- for such a long time! And here they are, 2 dreamy versions, available for pre-order on the 31st of August!

My main vision, was to make something that could be passed down for generations, and have the sight of it on your bookshelf sweep you off your broom.

The Grimoire Regal version, is made of hardcover synthetic leather and gold foil, and inside, the most unique, handmade paper with deckle edges.

The Grimoire Noble edition, has the same exterior in a smaller size (still pretty big!) gilded edges and 115gsm paper inside.

These Grimoires go hand in hand with this year’s planner 🙊♥️
